# GROWcery Project

- Project: GROWcery
- Language: TypeScript
- Framework: Next.js (App Router)
- ORM: Drizzle ORM
- Auth: Clerk
- Styling: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui

# Used patterns
- Client components load data using useSWR. This loads data through client API. The client API gets the data from API. The API loads the data from a query.
- When a client component need to save data then uses the useAction hook. 